'''雅利安·伐爾塔'''（[[梵語|梵語]]：{{lang|sa|आर्यावर्त}}，{{IAST|''Āryāvarta''}}），含義為高貴者的領土<ref>《Monier Williams Sanskrit-English Dictionary》：m."abode of the noble or excellent ones"</ref>，或[[雅利安人|雅利安人]]的神聖國土<ref>《Monier Williams Sanskrit-English Dictionary》：m. the sacred land of the Aryans (Name of Northern and Central India, extending from the eastern to the western sea and bounded on the north and south by the himālaya - and vindhya - mountains)</ref>，在古[[梵語|梵語]]中是指[[北印度|北印度]]。是由[[喜馬拉雅山|喜馬拉雅山]]的[[犍陀羅|犍陀羅]]至[[溫迪亞山脈|溫迪亞山脈]]，[[孟加拉灣|孟加拉灣]]至[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]。

